<HEADLINE>
VERNON WELLS' ADVANCEMENT HAS BEEN ANYTHING BUT SLOW
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By SIMON GONZALEZ 
c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
