<SLUG> BC-HEALTH-HYSTERIA08-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    SCIENCE/HEALTH: Irradiating solid foods safe, but there are
still naysayers
 &HT;    By Kevin Lamb
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   DAYTON, Ohio _ If the news media had transmitted hysteria as
effectively in the mid-1800s as they do now, 19th century crusaders
might have saved the world from the evils of pasteurized milk.
</P>
