   AUTOMOTIVE
</P>
<P>
   COXNET WHEELS PAGE
</P>
<P>
   EDs: This is the CoxNet WHEELS page for the current week. This
layout is availabletoday after 3 p.m. EST.
</P>
<P>
   COXNET WHEELS 0307 -- For anyone who's about to venture into
real unpaved territory and wants a vehicle that's thoroughly tough,
there's nothing quite like the Land Rover Discovery II. (DeVault,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution) Art includes 4-column color photo of
the 2000 Land Rover Discovery II.
</P>
<P>
