<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-07 13:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9332 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f BC-ECOM-RETAILERS-BOS &LR;      03-07 1789
