<P>
   MUSIC CONFERENCE DISCOVERS THE INTERNET: Four years ago, the
Internet was no more prevalent at the South by Southwest Music
Conference than any of the hundreds of bands vying for attention at
Austin's annual hyperspasm of cool. Even worse, it was still
largely seen as a geek's tool.This year, it's all you hear about.
