<P>
   ELLIOTT FULL OF DRIVE IN YEAR 25: On Feb. 29, 1976, Bill Elliott
showed up at Rockingham, N.C., with a second-hand Ford Torino and a
desire to become a Winston Cup racer. Few people would have
imagined that the skinny kid with the bushy red hair would one day
rule Winston Cup racing _ or that he would be raising eyebrows with
his competitiveness in his 25th season. (Includes a photo of Bill
Elliott.)
</P>
