<P>
   UNDATED _ A serious question for you, dear reader, one that I
have no answer to and that currently keeps the Post Toasties in my
belly all aflutter: Is there any way to keep my 5-year-old daughter
from becoming a female? By ERIC CELESTE. Story has moved in ``l''
lifestyle category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   TRIVIA-Q&AMP;A &QL;
</P>
