<HEADLINE>
KEY RATES 
</HEADLINE>
  (mk) 
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the daily key rates from The New York Times.
</P>
<P>
   --------------------Tuesday-----Monday-------Year Ago
</P>
