   PRIME RATE ---------- 8.75 ------ 8.75 ------- 7.75
</P>
<P>
   DISCOUNT RATE ------- 5.25 ------ 5.25 ------- 4.50
</P>
<P>
   FEDERAL FUNDS(x) ---- 5.69------ 5.73------- 4.73
</P>
<P>
   3-MO. TREAS. BILLS -- 5.65 ------ 5.69 ------- 4.53
</P>
<P>
   6-MO. TREAS. BILLS -- 5.78 ------ 5.82 ------- 4.55
</P>
<P>
   10-YR. TREAS. INF(xx) 4.21 ------ 4.23 ------- 3.86
</P>
<P>
