scheduled for AMs of Wednesday, 03/08/2000. They are available to
all NYT graphic clients via satellite on Associated Press
GraphicsNet, and will be posted on PressLink, Newscom and the Wieck
PhotoDatabase bulletin boards. For retransmission of graphics from
