<P>
   Attention graphic editors:
</P>
<P>
   A new weather package is being prepared by the New York Times
News Service. The launch date is scheduled for March 20.
</P>
<P>
   The new map will measure 52p x 6. Cloud cover information will
be incorporated into the new map which also highlights more cities.
</P>
<P>
   The region covered by the map has been extended to cover
northern Mexico and the Canadian border region.
</P>
<P>
   The news service will continue to provide a black and white
version as well as color. The colors on the new map will remain the
same.
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
