<P>
   HKN-BRUINS-MCLAREN (Boston) _ There was no ceremony or formal
passing of the torch by Ray Bourque to Kyle McLaren, the new
minister of defense for the Boston Bruins. By Nick Cafardo.
</P>
<P>
