   BUSH-NOMINATION (Austin, Texas) _ Battered, bruised and out of
money, George W. Bush is poised to clinch the GOP nomination with
victories in Republican contests in two states _ Texas and Florida.
Both states hold primaries next week. By R.G. RATCLIFFE.
