record four years for the Senate to decide on his nomination to the
9th U.S. Circuit Court of Appeals. Paez still faces a close vote.
Although he has the support of all 45 Democratic senators, most of
the 55 Republicans oppose his nomination. By MARK HELM and JUDY
HOLLAND.
